title: Aragorn VS Witch King: Battle of the Dead Marshes - Total War: Rise of Mordor Mod Gameplay
description:
Aragorn VS Witch King: Battle of the Dead Marshes - Total War: Rise of Mordor Mod Gameplay - Today we are looking at another battle in Rise of Mordor.  We are using the sub mod called Galadhrim Elves.  The mod has been recently updated and you can now fight with Agragorn, Witch-King, and Sauron.  In this battle Sauron leads his great legions of darkness against Aragorn's Army.  The battle is at the Dead Marshes.  Rise of Mordor is a Mod for Total War Attila based on the Lord of the Rings. Enjoy the Battle :D

Jackie's Channel: https://www.youtube.com/user/Jackiefishhhhhh

Mods:
Map - https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=675921047&searchtext=marsh

Elves -  https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=902039224&searchtext=elves

Lighting Mod - https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=532125259&searchtext=aztec+mod

If you enjoyed the video don't forget to Like and Leave a comment :D
